---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="NFT & Purchase Terms — Rift Wars" description="NFT minting, purchase terms, and digital asset policies for Rift Wars.">
  <section class="section-padding pt-32 bg-mm-bg">
    <div class="section-container max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="font-orbitron text-3xl font-bold text-mm-text mb-8 neon-text">NFT & Purchase Terms</h1>

      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-6">
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2">Last updated: April 2, 2026</p>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed">
          These terms govern the purchase, minting, and ownership of digital assets in the Rift Wars ecosystem,
          operated by <strong>Meta Machina Studio LLC</strong>. By purchasing or minting any digital asset,
          you agree to these terms in addition to our <a href="/terms" class="text-mm-cyan hover:underline">Terms of Service</a>.
          You must be 18 years or older to make any purchase.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-orbitron text-lg text-mm-cyan mt-8 mb-3">1. Genesis Card Packs</h2>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed">
          Genesis Packs contain 7 NFT cards minted on the blockchain. There is a maximum supply of
          <strong>2,000,000 Genesis Packs</strong> (14,000,000 total cards). Once all packs are minted, no more will be created.
        </p>
        <ul class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed list-disc ml-6 space-y-1">
          <li><strong>Price:</strong> 300 M-Credz per pack. Both M-Credz and crypto payment methods draw from the same supply.</li>
          <li><strong>Contents:</strong> Slots 1-5: Common (guaranteed). Slot 6: Rare (guaranteed). Slot 7 (Wild Slot): 55% Rare, 40% Epic, 4.5% Legendary, 0.5% God Tier.</li>
          <li><strong>On-chain:</strong> Cards are minted as compressed NFTs (cNFTs) on the Solana blockchain using the Metaplex Bubblegum standard.</li>
          <li><strong>Art storage:</strong> Card art is uploaded to Arweave via Irys for permanent, decentralized storage.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="font-orbitron text-lg text-mm-cyan mt-8 mb-3">2. What You Own</h2>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed">
          When you mint or purchase an NFT card, you own the on-chain token. This grants you:
        </p>
        <ul class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed list-disc ml-6 space-y-1">
          <li>The right to use the card in Rift Wars gameplay</li>
          <li>The right to display the card art for personal, non-commercial purposes (e.g., social media profile pictures, personal collections)</li>
          <li>The right to sell, trade, or transfer the NFT on authorized secondary markets</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed">
          <strong>Meta Machina Studio LLC retains all underlying intellectual property rights</strong> to the card art,
          character designs, names, lore, and game content. You may not use the art for commercial purposes (merchandise,
          products, advertising) without written permission. You may not claim authorship of the art or misrepresent
          your relationship with Meta Machina.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-orbitron text-lg text-mm-cyan mt-8 mb-3">3. Animated Hero Portraits</h2>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed">
          Animated Hero Portraits are premium NFTs featuring living, animated versions of hero art.
        </p>
        <ul class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed list-disc ml-6 space-y-1">
          <li><strong>Price:</strong> $50.00 USD each. Limited availability.</li>
          <li><strong>Process:</strong> This is a custom service. Portraits are animated using AI tools, quality-reviewed, then minted and delivered to the buyer's wallet and in-game vault. There is a queue — delivery is not instant.</li>
          <li><strong>Use:</strong> Purely cosmetic. Usable as your in-game hero portrait and profile display. No gameplay advantage.</li>
          <li><strong>Ownership:</strong> You own the NFT. Same IP terms as card NFTs above — personal use licensed, commercial rights retained by Meta Machina Studio LLC.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="font-orbitron text-lg text-mm-cyan mt-8 mb-3">4. M-Credz (In-Game Currency)</h2>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed">
          M-Credz is the in-game utility currency of Rift Wars. M-Credz are:
        </p>
        <ul class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed list-disc ml-6 space-y-1">
          <li><strong>Not a security</strong> and not an investment vehicle</li>
          <li><strong>Not designed for speculation</strong> — the peg is fixed, there is no price appreciation mechanism</li>
          <li><strong>Soulbound</strong> when launched on-chain — non-transferable between players, cannot be listed on DEXs or traded peer-to-peer</li>
          <li><strong>Elastic supply</strong> — minted on demand, burned on spend, to prevent hoarding</li>
          <li><strong>Blockchain:</strong> Chain pending (not yet launched on-chain). Currently in-game only during beta.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="font-orbitron text-lg text-mm-cyan mt-8 mb-3">5. Battle Pass</h2>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed">
          Battle Pass subscriptions unlock enhanced earning (uncapped M-Credz), bonus packs, and cosmetic rewards.
          Battle Pass purchases are non-refundable. Battle Pass benefits apply for the duration of the active season.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-orbitron text-lg text-mm-cyan mt-8 mb-3">6. Secondary Market & Royalties</h2>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed">
          All NFT card trades on secondary markets carry an immutable <strong>1% creator royalty</strong> hardcoded into the
          smart contract, payable to the Meta Machina Studio LLC treasury. This royalty is non-negotiable and applies to
          all secondary sales regardless of marketplace.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-orbitron text-lg text-mm-cyan mt-8 mb-3">7. Ante System (Future)</h2>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed">
          A future Ante system will allow players to stake cards of the same rarity in competitive matches.
          The winner takes the staked cards. Ante matches are entirely optional and involve risk of losing your NFT cards.
          By participating in Ante matches, you accept full responsibility for any cards lost. Further terms will be
          published when this feature launches.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-orbitron text-lg text-mm-cyan mt-8 mb-3">8. Card Burning</h2>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed">
          Players may burn duplicate Common and Rare cards to receive M-Credz. Burning is permanent and irreversible —
          the NFT is destroyed on-chain. Burn values are set by the game and may be adjusted.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-orbitron text-lg text-mm-cyan mt-8 mb-3">9. Refund Policy</h2>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed">
          <strong>All sales are final. No refunds.</strong> This applies to:
        </p>
        <ul class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed list-disc ml-6 space-y-1">
          <li>Genesis Pack mints</li>
          <li>M-Credz purchases</li>
          <li>Battle Pass subscriptions</li>
          <li>Animated Portrait commissions</li>
          <li>Any other digital goods or services</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed">
          Blockchain transactions are irreversible by design. We cannot reverse, cancel, or modify completed on-chain transactions.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-orbitron text-lg text-mm-cyan mt-8 mb-3">10. Risk Acknowledgment</h2>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed">By purchasing digital assets, you acknowledge:</p>
        <ul class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed list-disc ml-6 space-y-1">
          <li>NFTs and digital assets have no guaranteed monetary value on secondary markets</li>
          <li>Blockchain technology involves inherent risks including smart contract bugs, network congestion, and wallet security</li>
          <li>You are solely responsible for the security of your wallet and private keys</li>
          <li>Game balance changes may affect the in-game utility of specific cards</li>
          <li>We are not responsible for losses due to user error, phishing, wallet compromise, or third-party marketplace issues</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="font-orbitron text-lg text-mm-cyan mt-8 mb-3">11. Service Discontinuation</h2>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed">
          If Rift Wars ceases operations, players retain ownership of their NFTs on the blockchain. Card art stored on
          Arweave is permanent and decentralized — it persists independently of our servers at the discretion of the
          Arweave network. On-chain token ownership is immutable regardless of game server status.
          We make no guarantees about the continued availability of game servers, in-game functionality, or the
          ongoing utility of NFTs within the game.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-orbitron text-lg text-mm-cyan mt-8 mb-3">12. Contact</h2>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed">
          Meta Machina Studio LLC<br />
          Email: <a href="mailto:legal@metamachina.io" class="text-mm-cyan hover:underline">legal@metamachina.io</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
